{"title":"Pilot Scram Ti Gravel Bike First w/ Pinion Smart.Shift","link":"https://bikerumor.com/pilot-scram-pinion-gravel-bike/","date":1705932861000,"content":"<p><img width=\"2000\" height=\"1335\" src=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/Pilot-Scram-Pinion-SmartShift-titanium-gravel-bike-1.jpg\" alt=\"side view of pilot scram pinion titanium gravel bike\" loading=\"lazy\" srcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/Pilot-Scram-Pinion-SmartShift-titanium-gravel-bike-1.jpg 2000w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/Pilot-Scram-Pinion-SmartShift-titanium-gravel-bike-1-297x198.jpg 297w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/Pilot-Scram-Pinion-SmartShift-titanium-gravel-bike-1-800x533.jpg 800w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/Pilot-Scram-Pinion-SmartShift-titanium-gravel-bike-1-120x80.jpg 120w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/Pilot-Scram-Pinion-SmartShift-titanium-gravel-bike-1-768x513.jpg 768w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/Pilot-Scram-Pinion-SmartShift-titanium-gravel-bike-1-1536x1025.jpg 1536w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/Pilot-Scram-Pinion-SmartShift-titanium-gravel-bike-1-720x480.jpg 720w\" /></p>\n<p>The new Pilot Scram Pinion is the world’s first gravel bike with Pinion’s electronic Smart.Shift gear box. And it’s paired with Gates’ CDX Belt Drive and titanium frame for ultra-low maintenance all around.</p>\n\n\n\n<p><a href=\"https://pinion.eu/en/smartshift\" target=\"_blank\">Pinion’s Smart.Shift</a> debuted in 2022 for e-bikes, pulling power from their battery. Then in 2023, they launched this standalone unit with it’s own battery and Priority Cycles launched <a href=\"https://bikerumor.com/priority-bikes-600hxt-pinion-smart-shift-tech/\" target=\"_blank\">the first mountain bike with it</a> that summer. This is the first drop bar bike to use it.</p>\n\n\n\n<figure><a href=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/Pilot-Scram-Pinion-SmartShift-titanium-gravel-bike-7.jpg\"><img loading=\"lazy\" width=\"2000\" height=\"1336\" src=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/Pilot-Scram-Pinion-SmartShift-titanium-gravel-bike-7.jpg\" alt=\"closeup view of pilot scram pinion titanium gravel bike gearbox\" srcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/Pilot-Scram-Pinion-SmartShift-titanium-gravel-bike-7.jpg 2000w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/Pilot-Scram-Pinion-SmartShift-titanium-gravel-bike-7-297x198.jpg 297w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/Pilot-Scram-Pinion-SmartShift-titanium-gravel-bike-7-800x533.jpg 800w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/Pilot-Scram-Pinion-SmartShift-titanium-gravel-bike-7-120x80.jpg 120w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/Pilot-Scram-Pinion-SmartShift-titanium-gravel-bike-7-768x513.jpg 768w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/Pilot-Scram-Pinion-SmartShift-titanium-gravel-bike-7-1536x1026.jpg 1536w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/Pilot-Scram-Pinion-SmartShift-titanium-gravel-bike-7-720x480.jpg 720w\" /></a></figure>\n\n\n\n<p>The system combines Pinion’s internally geared gearbox at the cranks with electronic shifting, overcoming the original’s drawback of requiring two cables running from the shifter, replacing them with a single wire.</p>\n\n\n\n<figure><a href=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/Pilot-Scram-Pinion-SmartShift-titanium-gravel-bike-4.jpg\"><img loading=\"lazy\" width=\"2000\" height=\"1600\" src=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/Pilot-Scram-Pinion-SmartShift-titanium-gravel-bike-4.jpg\" alt=\"closeup view of pilot scram pinion titanium gravel bike gearbox\" srcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/Pilot-Scram-Pinion-SmartShift-titanium-gravel-bike-4.jpg 2000w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/Pilot-Scram-Pinion-SmartShift-titanium-gravel-bike-4-297x238.jpg 297w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/Pilot-Scram-Pinion-SmartShift-titanium-gravel-bike-4-800x640.jpg 800w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/Pilot-Scram-Pinion-SmartShift-titanium-gravel-bike-4-120x96.jpg 120w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/Pilot-Scram-Pinion-SmartShift-titanium-gravel-bike-4-768x614.jpg 768w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/Pilot-Scram-Pinion-SmartShift-titanium-gravel-bike-4-1536x1229.jpg 1536w\" /></a></figure>\n\n\n\n<p>It’s housed in a custom titanium shell, beautifully integrated into this frame’s design.</p>\n\n\n\n<figure><a href=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/Pilot-Scram-Pinion-SmartShift-titanium-gravel-bike-6.jpg\"><img loading=\"lazy\" width=\"2000\" height=\"1335\" src=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/Pilot-Scram-Pinion-SmartShift-titanium-gravel-bike-6.jpg\" alt=\"closeup view of pilot scram pinion titanium gravel bike TRP shifter levers\" srcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/Pilot-Scram-Pinion-SmartShift-titanium-gravel-bike-6.jpg 2000w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/Pilot-Scram-Pinion-SmartShift-titanium-gravel-bike-6-297x198.jpg 297w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/Pilot-Scram-Pinion-SmartShift-titanium-gravel-bike-6-800x533.jpg 800w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/Pilot-Scram-Pinion-SmartShift-titanium-gravel-bike-6-120x80.jpg 120w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/Pilot-Scram-Pinion-SmartShift-titanium-gravel-bike-6-768x513.jpg 768w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/Pilot-Scram-Pinion-SmartShift-titanium-gravel-bike-6-1536x1025.jpg 1536w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/Pilot-Scram-Pinion-SmartShift-titanium-gravel-bike-6-720x480.jpg 720w\" /></a></figure>\n\n\n\n<p>For drop bar bikes, it’s paired with TRP HyWire shifters and brakeset, which is a gamechanger for ergonomics compared to the mechanical twist shifter. Both brake hoses and the shift wires run internally through the frame, with a small charging port on the downtube.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>Pilot is using the Pinion C-line model with 12-speeds and rapid 0.2-second shifts. It can shift under load or at a standstill. You can even program a “starting gear” that it’ll automatically return to when you come to a stop, making take-off easier and at just the right cadence.</p>\n\n\n\n<figure><a href=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/Pilot-Scram-Pinion-SmartShift-titanium-gravel-bike-3.jpg\"><img loading=\"lazy\" width=\"2000\" height=\"1335\" src=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/Pilot-Scram-Pinion-SmartShift-titanium-gravel-bike-3.jpg\" alt=\"closeup view of pilot scram pinion titanium gravel bike dropouts\" srcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/Pilot-Scram-Pinion-SmartShift-titanium-gravel-bike-3.jpg 2000w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/Pilot-Scram-Pinion-SmartShift-titanium-gravel-bike-3-297x198.jpg 297w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/Pilot-Scram-Pinion-SmartShift-titanium-gravel-bike-3-800x533.jpg 800w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/Pilot-Scram-Pinion-SmartShift-titanium-gravel-bike-3-120x80.jpg 120w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/Pilot-Scram-Pinion-SmartShift-titanium-gravel-bike-3-768x513.jpg 768w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/Pilot-Scram-Pinion-SmartShift-titanium-gravel-bike-3-1536x1025.jpg 1536w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/Pilot-Scram-Pinion-SmartShift-titanium-gravel-bike-3-720x480.jpg 720w\" /></a></figure>\n\n\n\n<p>The bike uses sliding dropouts to tension the belt drive, with a bolt-together frame brake on the driveside seatstay.</p>\n\n\n\n<figure><a href=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/Pilot-Scram-Pinion-SmartShift-titanium-gravel-bike-2.jpg\"><img loading=\"lazy\" width=\"2000\" height=\"1335\" src=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/Pilot-Scram-Pinion-SmartShift-titanium-gravel-bike-2.jpg\" alt=\"side view of pilot scram pinion titanium gravel bike\" srcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/Pilot-Scram-Pinion-SmartShift-titanium-gravel-bike-2.jpg 2000w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/Pilot-Scram-Pinion-SmartShift-titanium-gravel-bike-2-297x198.jpg 297w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/Pilot-Scram-Pinion-SmartShift-titanium-gravel-bike-2-800x533.jpg 800w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/Pilot-Scram-Pinion-SmartShift-titanium-gravel-bike-2-120x80.jpg 120w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/Pilot-Scram-Pinion-SmartShift-titanium-gravel-bike-2-768x513.jpg 768w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/Pilot-Scram-Pinion-SmartShift-titanium-gravel-bike-2-1536x1025.jpg 1536w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/Pilot-Scram-Pinion-SmartShift-titanium-gravel-bike-2-720x480.jpg 720w\" /></a></figure>\n\n\n\n<p>The completely sealed gearbox and maintenance-free belt drive makes it a perfect adventure bike, and it has triple bottle bosses on the seat tube and both sides of the downtube, giving you plenty of storage options…</p>\n\n\n\n<figure><a href=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/Pilot-Scram-Pinion-SmartShift-titanium-gravel-bike-5.jpg\"><img loading=\"lazy\" width=\"1400\" height=\"2097\" src=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/Pilot-Scram-Pinion-SmartShift-titanium-gravel-bike-5.jpg\" alt=\"closeup view of pilot scram pinion titanium gravel bike seatstays\" srcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/Pilot-Scram-Pinion-SmartShift-titanium-gravel-bike-5.jpg 1400w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/Pilot-Scram-Pinion-SmartShift-titanium-gravel-bike-5-200x300.jpg 200w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/Pilot-Scram-Pinion-SmartShift-titanium-gravel-bike-5-800x1198.jpg 800w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/Pilot-Scram-Pinion-SmartShift-titanium-gravel-bike-5-80x120.jpg 80w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/Pilot-Scram-Pinion-SmartShift-titanium-gravel-bike-5-768x1150.jpg 768w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/Pilot-Scram-Pinion-SmartShift-titanium-gravel-bike-5-1025x1536.jpg 1025w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/Pilot-Scram-Pinion-SmartShift-titanium-gravel-bike-5-1367x2048.jpg 1367w\" /></a></figure>\n\n\n\n<p>…plus rack and fender mounts on the rear. Swap out the fork for something with Anything Cage mounts (or add <a href=\"https://bikerumor.com/first-look-old-man-mountain-axle-pack-puts-bikepacking-anything-cages-on-any-fork/\">Old Man Mountain’s new Axle Pack kit</a>) and you’re ready for bikepacking.</p>\n\n\n\n<figure><a href=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/Pilot-Scram-Pinion-geometry-chart.jpg\"><img loading=\"lazy\" width=\"2000\" height=\"652\" src=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/Pilot-Scram-Pinion-geometry-chart.jpg\" alt=\"pilot scram pinion geometry chart\" srcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/Pilot-Scram-Pinion-geometry-chart.jpg 2000w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/Pilot-Scram-Pinion-geometry-chart-297x97.jpg 297w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/Pilot-Scram-Pinion-geometry-chart-800x261.jpg 800w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/Pilot-Scram-Pinion-geometry-chart-120x39.jpg 120w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/Pilot-Scram-Pinion-geometry-chart-768x250.jpg 768w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/Pilot-Scram-Pinion-geometry-chart-1536x501.jpg 1536w\" /></a></figure>\n\n\n\n<p>It’ll be available as a frameset (€4,200) and complete bike (from €8,250) with the following spec:</p>\n\n\n\n<ul>\n<li><strong>Wheelset:</strong> OHR G2 / G45</li>\n\n\n\n<li><strong>Handlebar:</strong> Ritchey Venturemax</li>\n\n\n\n<li><strong>Seatpost:</strong> Ritchey 2-Bolt</li>\n\n\n\n<li><strong>Frame finish:</strong> Brushed Frame with Sandblasted Logos / custom logos</li>\n\n\n\n<li><strong>Fork:</strong> Pilot Carbon Gravel</li>\n\n\n\n<li><strong>Brakes and shifters:</strong> TRP HyWire</li>\n\n\n\n<li><strong>Tires:</strong> Vredestein Aventura / Grezzo 38 / 44mm</li>\n\n\n\n<li><strong>Wheels:</strong> OHR Cycling G2</li>\n</ul>\n\n\n\n<p><em><a href=\"https://www.pilotcycles.com/frame-customize/scram-pinion-smart-shift/\" target=\"_blank\">PilotCycles.com</a></em></p>\n<p>The post <a href=\"https://bikerumor.com/pilot-scram-pinion-gravel-bike/\">Pilot Scram Ti Gravel Bike First w/ Pinion Smart.Shift</a> appeared first on <a href=\"https://bikerumor.com\">Bikerumor</a>.</p>","author":"Tyler Benedict","siteTitle":"Bikerumor","siteHash":"49f427af0a926f4232eb837006841d7242e153e3afbb590f32e4b104ea3e2718","entryHash":"2687bf65c6d40b0d55daa9a3cb221fab73d0dcd7b157d955ee423504e352bde2","category":"Cycling"}